						<summary>

						<p>This records a gift of 30 <hi rend="italic">kaḻañju</hi> of gold left in charge of the <hi rend="italic">nagarattār</hi> (guild) of Tiruppaḻanam for the maintenance of a perpetual lamp in the temple of Mahādēva with the interest thereon, by <hi rend="bold">Nakkaṉ A[ri]ñjigai</hi> <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> <hi rend="bold">Parāntaka-Pallava[raiyaṉ].</hi> This is probably a record of <hi rend="bold">Uttama-Chōḷa.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
